# Built locally by src-native/windows/publish.ps1 for local development, and shipped to npm
# consumers via the NativeScript.FontManager NuGet package (see plugin.props). The binaries are
# never committed and are excluded from the npm package (see project.json assets) so npm pulls
# them from NuGet - mirroring Android (no committed .aar) and iOS (no committed framework).
